{"tid":2436081,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普前幕僚涉國會暴動 持盾牌衝撞大門防線","createTime":"2021-03-06T20:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T10:54:10.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ff34ce7ec164d15378147c85f9f36c372c0422bb","tid":2436081,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T20:26:00.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國1月6日發生國會大廈暴動案後，出現第1位川普國務院前幕僚被捕起訴，他是42歲的柯連（Federico Klein），曾任美國國務院特別助理，涉嫌妨礙國會運作、持危險武器攻擊員警等罪。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，暴動當天，警方配戴的攝影機捕捉多張柯連的影像，當天下午2點43分，他出現在暴動最前線，當時民眾試圖突破警方防線，穿越國會的兩道門。<br />\n<br />\n法院文件顯示，柯連當時手持鎮暴盾牌，企圖強行進入國會的門，他還數次大喊，要求民眾前來支援。之後警方動用噴霧劑，才將他強行移往它處。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n賽希莉亞說，科連曾是海軍陸戰隊員，還被派駐到伊拉克，是個聰明誠實的好孩子，但她不喜歡他為川普工作。<br />\n<br />\n據美國官方資料，柯連2004年1月至2012年11月在美國海軍陸戰隊服役，在2005年2月至9月被派到伊拉克執行任務。<br />\n<br />\n柯連2016加入川普競選團隊，2017年開始任美國國務院助理，一直到拜登宣誓就職（1月20日）的前一天才辭職。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3458584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3458584&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=8ab3c069\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3458584&h=20630298\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3458584</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www-insideedition-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/www.insideedition.com/sites/default/files/styles/1129x570/public/images/2021-03/030521_cop_tunnel_web.jpg?h=d1cb525d&amp;itok=gIkAFzY_\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-insideedition-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fwww.insideedition.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2F1129x570%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2021-03%2F030521_cop_tunnel_web.jpg%3Fh%3Dd1cb525d%26itok%3DgIkAFzY_&h=0af4ee82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁高級都咁勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6cb26389c4320b5a52c7a5ce4d84ca5f71a7cc","tid":2436081,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T20:33:32.000Z","msg":"想煲成衝國會暴力過殺人放火"},{"pid":"ddc7c7b93be3e1aa0bcf832ff877adbc6253bb46","tid":2436081,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:46:47.000Z","msg":"拜登 = 司馬懿<br />\n侵侵 = 曹爽<br />\n<br />\n司馬懿 政變成功掌權之後, 就開始清算 曹爽既親信"},{"pid":"40d2443f5811cec573237317ad30b81cd9c32cab","tid":2436081,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}